Description

About This Product

Set the stage for a good night’s sleep with this medium plush hybrid mattress with edge support. It is crafted using a six-layer combination of pocket coils and gel memory foam and features a medium firmness with low motion transfer – so your partner’s movements won’t disturb your rest. What’s more, it has a breathable, hypoallergenic design that’s ideal for sensitive sleepers and boasts a quilted euro-top knit cover with a corded edge. It is designed to rest on box springs or directly on slats and is compatible with an adjustable bed. This mattress ships compressed in a box, so please allow up to 48 hrs. for it to inflate fully before use.

Features

Combines the superior support of a wrapped-coil innerspring system with the conforming response of gel-infused memory foam
Discover our collection of affordable mattresses and bedding basics, with reliable features proven to please. With a 100-night free trial on mattresses and budget-friendly prices, you can rest easier
Cooling technology: Regulates your body temperature throughout the night, ensuring you stay cool and comfortable, even on the hottest nights
Breathable design: Not only are our mattresses built to allow for optimum airflow, but they are designed with only the highest standards. We use natural fire barriers instead of harsh chemicals, and all of our foams are CertiPUR-US® and OEKO-TEX® Certified ensuring no harmful off-gassing, VOCs or harmful toxins interrupt your sleep
Low motion transfer: Designed to minimize disturbances caused by tossing and turning
Optimized edge support: Crafted to provide uniform comfort even when sitting or sleeping close to the edge, our mattress eliminates any sagging, ensuring peaceful rest in any position
Optimized edge support: Crafted to provide uniform comfort even when sitting or sleeping close to the edge
Lumbar support: Designed to specifically target and support the lower back, promoting proper spinal alignment and reducing the risk of discomfort and pain
Lumbar support: Designed to specifically target and support the lower back
Cooling Comfort: Regulates body temperature for a cool, restful night, even in warm conditions
Adjustable friendly: Compatible with adjustable base (sold separately)
Customized Support: Adapts to your body's contours for orthopedic, personalized comfort
Breathable and Safe: Allows airflow with natural fire barriers and CertiPUR-US & OEKO-TEX Certified foams—no harmful chemicals or toxins
Shop sustainably: Sustainably sourced and produced – our commitment to protect our planet and shared home to build an environmentally sustainable future for all
